modName: College of Winterhold - More Interior Doors
summary: This will add doors to the rooms in the Hall of Attainment and Hall of Countenance in the College of Winterhold.
descriptionHtml:
[b]This will add doors to the rooms in the Hall of Attainment and Hall of Countenance in the College of Winterhold.[/b]

One thing I didn't like about the interior structure of the College was the lack of doors.
This mod aims to fix that, check the screenshots and see if it's right for you!

[b]Things you should know:[/b]
Only one side of each door has a handle, not my fault.
People walk around more than you know, and doors are left open. This may look weird.

Currently, there is no quest to have them added. Just install the .esp and go!

If you liked this mod, I recommend:
Aldous the Alteration Mage adds two voiced NPCs with quests to populate the College.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25681/

---------------------------------
Compatibilities :

Any other mods that altar " WinterholdAnimDoor01 " may cause a conflict.
author: Thynar

files.name: SAM WinterholdDoors Inward
files.changelogHtml: Reversed doors, they open inward to rooms now, no other changes. Feel free to pick this or the 1.00 version.
